latestIgtvVideos.title: Bday 2021
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Last year 2020, my bday was the last outing we did before the lockdown. Though this year there was no lockdown, I did continue the trend of making my special day a family day. If one thing i have learnt out of the pandemic is that everyone else may leave you but it’s the family that stays and that matters!!!
Ty @sankalppardeshi and @rudransh_pardeshi for planning the surprise bday gift for me!
Ty @ninad.pardeshi bhaiya @jagz_____ bhabhi @isahebsingh bhaiya @angelmannangel bhabhi for making it special with presence!
Ty @vviniaggarwall for the amazing gift u planned and made sure it reached me on time.
Ty @deep_pillay_ @naidunamita ❤️
I did realise that I have some friends whom I can call family as well... and that’s @kreetika10 ty for the lovely surprise!!
